This directory contains files for building the linux-live spooky scoreboard installer.
The installer is built using Linux Live Kit.
See https://github.com/Tomas-M/linux-live for more information.
The latest, pre-built, ready-to-flash installer is available at https://scoreboard.web.net/ssbd-installer.zip

How to build installer image.
1. Run `docker build -t ssbd-installer -f Dockerfile ../` from this directory to build the installer.
2. Run `docker run --privileged -it ssbd`
3. ...
